{"tid":2074485,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全天候跟蹤黎智英 多名退役警策劃  「中共暗殺」直幡掛連儂崖","createTime":"2020-06-22T06:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T10:28:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c6ab8235351310077d1343958acfba7407ec4acb","tid":2074485,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T06:40:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200622/QJAJ5F4A2ATS5LNM4GXUMLZBD4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200622%2FQJAJ5F4A2ATS5LNM4GXUMLZBD4%2F&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F8lSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=318c71a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200622%2FQJAJ5F4A2ATS5LNM4GXUMLZBD4%2F&h=9431135a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200622/QJAJ5F4A2ATS5LNM4GXUMLZBD4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n全天候跟蹤黎智英 多名退役警策劃 <br />\n「中共暗殺」直幡掛連儂崖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港版國安法陰霾下香港瀰漫白色恐怖，筆架山昨出現一幅寫有「中共計劃暗殺黎智英」直幡，抗議暴政。壹傳媒創辦人黎智英已連續第六日遭神秘人跟蹤，兩輛黑白七人車繼續在黎宅外守候，又尾隨黎的座駕外出。繼早前有跟蹤者自稱「真傳媒服務公司」資料搜集員，但被揭與資深警員同名同姓後，本報再獲得消息，觀塘一間由多名退役警包括前警司開設的偵探社涉及跟蹤事件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QYHF3IVUISEETBT4HWSQR2JAKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQYHF3IVUISEETBT4HWSQR2JAKU.jpg&h=e080a565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n筆架山昨現一幅約兩米乘20米、寫上「中共計劃暗殺黎智英」的直幡。<br />\n<br />\n黎智英遭神秘人24小時跟蹤，昨踏入第六日，兩輛黑色七人車UY2495及白色七人車US8045，車上分別載乘三名神秘男子，繼續在嘉道理道黎宅外守候。記者在場追訪，但對方各人封口拒回應。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大規模行動料日耗10萬<br />\n<br />\n昨日早上約10時，黎智英離開寓所乘座駕外出，其間白色七。。。。。有跟隨，續泊黎宅外。<br />\n<br />\n至下午，兩輛黑白七人車仍停在黎宅附近，記者再次上前查問，。。。。。度問記者：「（嘉道理道）下面係咪太子道西？」之後離去。<br />\n<br />\n記者連日發現24小時追蹤黎智英的神秘人，最少出動五部車輛，。。。。。料每日花費近10萬元，相信不可能由單一公司或偵探社包辦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KPIWPMJ5X4AZJSS3BIJ2MHGMSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKPIWPMJ5X4AZJSS3BIJ2MHGMSY.jpg&h=f0cd7370&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑色七人車司機封口拒回應記者的提問。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7WMIUP7FTVY7EPJKVGLYJCHVLQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7WMIUP7FTVY7EPJKVGLYJCHVLQ.jpg&h=0c8e0a68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一輛白色車停在黎宅外，一名男子下車抽煙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XZKWQZ32PTQQVQYV5ZUU7UFCFU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXZKWQZ32PTQQVQYV5ZUU7UFCFU.jpg&h=4f703953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎智英已連續第六日被神秘人跟蹤。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n偵探公司股東包括前警司<br />\n<br />\n業界消息傳出，跟蹤黎智英的神秘人包括觀塘一間由多名退。。。。。解事件，但疑因周末，未見有人辦公，電話亦無人接聽。<br />\n<br />\n此外，昨晨約6時，龍欣道。。。。。"},{"pid":"1a22696a711590c7ccdeb1a363638c488a84ce9d","tid":2074485,"uid":77092,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T06:50:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"253a963294db31834690a6e911fe03dc8baae3e6","tid":2074485,"uid":58209,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T06:51:20.000Z","msg":"做埋啲小動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344ab10d51e24fe58a0b02920cd18aa2d911a5d3","tid":2074485,"uid":17008,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T06:51:55.000Z","msg":"咁同公開中共暴行有乜分別"},{"pid":"69af3db056d30bf2416bf6e366beb7e3d40db0b6","tid":2074485,"uid":311128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T06:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93de7bacc574342fcd134f1f93052d94f3f783ae","tid":2074485,"uid":201605,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"cite